AKA: Filtering, Blocking
Filtering and moderation are topics which are close enough in intent as to be combined into one topic.
Moderation and filtering are concepts whereby a control entity has the power to censor according to their preferences. This power is used to avoid or remove persons or items which are extreme or innappropriate, and also to enforce rules and limits, as well as to censor content a 
